Figure 4a, b shows the detectivity and responsivity values of CsPbI2Br and CsPbIBr2 perovskite photodetectors measured at different incident light power. For CsPbI2Br device, under weak (3.5 mW/cm2) and strong (6 mW/cm2) illumination, D* were calculated to be 4.9 × 1011 and 3.2 × 1011 Jones (Jones=cm×Hz12×W-1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
